#. type: Title =
#: _guides/agent-mcp.adoc
msgid "Overview"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/agent-mcp.adoc
msgid ""
"The https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus-agent-mcp[Quarkus Agent MCP] server is a standalone Model Context Protocol (MCP) server that provides AI coding agents with a complete Quarkus development experience.\n"
"This is the **recommended** way to integrate AI coding agents with Quarkus applications."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/agent-mcp.adoc
msgid "The Quarkus Agent MCP server acts as a comprehensive development assistant, offering:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/agent-mcp.adoc
msgid "**Project scaffolding** — Create new Quarkus applications with customizable extensions"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/agent-mcp.adoc
msgid "**Application lifecycle management** — Start, stop, and restart your application, with automatic recovery from crashes"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/agent-mcp.adoc
msgid "**Dev MCP proxy** — Access all xref:dev-mcp.adoc[Dev MCP] tools from the running application"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/agent-mcp.adoc
msgid "**Documentation search** — Semantic search across Quarkus documentation using RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/agent-mcp.adoc
msgid "**Extension skills** — Get extension-specific coding patterns, best practices, and testing guidelines"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/agent-mcp.adoc
msgid "**Version management** — Check for updates and get upgrade reports"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title =
#: _guides/agent-mcp.adoc
msgid "Installation"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/agent-mcp.adoc
msgid ""
"The Quarkus Agent MCP server requires https://www.jbang.dev[JBang].\n"
"Make sure JBang is installed before configuring your agent:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/agent-mcp.adoc
msgid "If JBang is not installed, follow the instructions at https://www.jbang.dev/download/[jbang.dev/download]."
msgstr ""

